0, \"to\": 3241}]}, {\"sentence\": \"People love it when a dressage horse or a badminton rally goes viral.\", \"from\": 3243, \"to\": 3312, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"People\", \"from\": 3243, \"to\": 3249}, {\"ngram\": \"a dressage horse\", \"from\": 3263, \"to\": 3279}, {\"ngram\": \"a badminton rally\", \"from\": 3283, \"to\": 3300}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But NBC\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s prime-time coverage still focuses so much on the biggest sports and most famous athletes, with maybe a few highlights from elsewhere.Gold Zone\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s multiscreen capabilities and longer runtime lend space to invest a bit of time just to see what might happen\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094as well as the good sense to know you can\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t pull away when a wild ending in a France vs. Germany handball game falls in your lap.\", \"from\": 3313, \"to\": 3714, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3674, \"end\": 3681, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"score\": 0.9999441481922855, \"rank\": 5.584227429143022e-05, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"NBC\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s prime-time coverage\", \"from\": 3317, \"to\": 3344}, {\"ngram\": \"the biggest sports\", \"from\": 3370, \"to\": 3388}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 3405, \"to\": 3413}, {\"ngram\": \"maybe a few highlights\", \"from\": 3420, \"to\": 3442}, {\"ngram\": \"Gold Zone\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s multiscreen capabilities\", \"from\": 3458, \"to\": 3496}, {\"ngram\": \"longer runtime\", \"from\": 3501, \"to\": 3515}, {\"ngram\": \"space\", \"from\": 3521, \"to\": 3526}, {\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 3537, \"to\": 3542}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 3546, \"to\": 3550}, {\"ngram\": \"the good sense\", \"from\": 3594, \"to\": 3608}, {\"ngram\": \"a wild ending\", \"from\": 3644, \"to\": 3657}, {\"ngram\": \"your lap\", \"fr