 {\"sentence\": \"But an event doesn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t have to be for a medal to capture the attention of our Olympics concierges.\", \"from\": 4064, \"to\": 4162, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an event\", \"from\": 4068, \"to\": 4076}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 4102, \"to\": 4109}, {\"ngram\": \"the attention\", \"from\": 4121, \"to\": 4134}, {\"ngram\": \"our Olympics concierges\", \"from\": 4138, \"to\": 4161}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s been fun watching them seamlessly glide from fencing to archery to canoe slalom, sometimes learning the rules right along with viewers, without missing any of the truly crucial moments in swimming or gymnastics.\", \"from\": 4163, \"to\": 4381, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"archery\", \"from\": 4226, \"to\": 4233}, {\"ngram\": \"canoe slalom\", \"from\": 4237, \"to\": 4249}, {\"ngram\": \"the rules\", \"from\": 4270, \"to\": 4279}, {\"ngram\": \"viewers\", \"from\": 4297, \"to\": 4304}, {\"ngram\": \"the truly crucial moments\", \"from\": 4329, \"to\": 4354}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming\", \"from\": 4358, \"to\": 4366}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnastics\", \"from\": 4370, \"to\": 4380}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The show is also different at different times of day.\", \"from\": 4383, \"to\": 4436, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The show\", \"from\": 4383, \"to\": 4391}, {\"ngram\": \"different times\", \"from\": 4413, \"to\": 4428}, {\"ngram\": \"day\", \"from\": 4432, \"to\": 4435}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Iseman and Collinsworth captain a true morning show.\", \"from\": 4437, \"to\": 4489, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Iseman and Collinsworth captain\", \"from\": 4437, \"to\": 4468}, {\"ngram\": \"a true morning show\", \"from\": 4469, \"to\": 4488}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They appear at 7 a.m. to recap the early-morning action you may have missed, then talk about their coffee and show photos of pets watchingGold Zone.\", \"from\": 4490, \"to\": 4638, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"7 a.m.\", \"from\": 4505, \"to\": 4511}, {\"ngram\": \"the early-morning action\", \"from\": 4521, \"to\": 4545}, {\"ngram\": \"their coffee\", \"from\": 4583, \"to\": 4595}, {\"ngram\": \"photos\", \"from\": 4605, \"to\": 4611}, {\"ngram\": \"pets\", \"from\": 4615, \"to\": 4619}, {\"ngram\": \"watchingGold Zone\", \"from\": 4620, \"to\": 4637}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Siciliano and Hanson get more down to business during a time of day when more of the critical medal events seem to air in quick succession.\", \"from\": 4639, \"to\": 4778, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4653, \"end\": 4659, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tommy_Hanson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6125909380760533e-17, \"text\": \"Hanson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tommy_Hanson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tommy_Hanson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Siciliano\", \"from\": 4639, \"to\": 4648}, {\"ngram\": \"business\", \"from\": 4677, \"to\": 4685}, {\"ngram\": \"a time\", \"from\": 4693, \"to\": 4699}, {\"ngram\": \"day\", \"from\": 4703, \"to\": 4706}, {\"ngram\": \"the critical medal events\", \"from\": 4720, \"to\": 4745}, {\"ngram\": \"quick succession\", \"from\": 4761, \"to\": 4777}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The morning guys have time to fence against each other and bring in kids for a taekwondo demonstration.\", \"from\": 4779, \"to\": 4882, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The morning guys\", \"from\": 4779, \"to\": 4795}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 4801, \"to\": 4805}, {\"ngram\": \"kids\", \"from\": 4847, \"to\": 4851}, {\"ngram\": \"a taekwondo demonstration\", \"from\": 4856, \"to\": 4881}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hanson often feels like he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s still living inRedZone\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s witching hour.\", \"from\": 4883, \"to\": 4955, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hanson\", \"from\": 4883, \"to\": 4889}, {\"ngram\": \"he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 4907, \"to\": 4913}, {\"ngram\": \"witching hour\", \"from\": 4941, \"to\": 4954}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Iseman and Collinsworth come off like longtime buddies, but they had actually never met until three days before the first show.\", \"from\": 4957, \"to\": 5084, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Iseman\", \"from\": 4957, \"to\": 4963}, {\"ngram\": \"Collinsworth\", \"from\": 4968, \"to\": 4980}, {\"ngram\": \"longtime buddies\", \"from\": 4995, \"to\": 5011}, {\"ngram\": \"the first show\", \"from\": 5069, \"to\": 5083}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They seem to have become best friends faster than Will Ferrell and John C. Reilly inStep Brothers.\", \"from\": 5085, \"to\": 5183, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"best friends\", \"from\": 5110, \"to\": 5122}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Iseman says much of what you see on air has come together organically.\", \"from\": 5185, \"to\": 5255, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Iseman\", \"from\": 5185, \"to\": 5191}, {\"ngram\": \"air\", \"from\": 5221, \"to\": 5224}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cOn Friday afternoon [before Day 1], Jac and I were talking, none of us knew what the show would be.\", \"from\": 5256, \"to\": 5358, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cOn\", \"from\": 5256, \"to\": 5261}, {\"ngram\": \"Day\", \"from\": 5287, \"to\": 5290}, {\"ngram\": \"Jac\", \"from\": 5295, \"to\": 5298}, {\"ngram\": \"none\", \"from\": 5319, \"to\": 5323}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 5327, \"to\": 5329}, {\"ngram\": \"the show\", \"from\": 5340, \"to\": 5348}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You have an idea, but nobody\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s tried to simultaneously stream up to 40 events at a time, in dozens of different sports, and have it make sense.\", \"from\": 5359, \"to\": 5504, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an idea\", \"from\": 5368, \"to\": 5375}, {\"ngram\": \"nobody\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 5381, \"to\": 5391}, {\"ngram\": \"up to 40 events\", \"from\": 5423, \"to\": 5438}, {\"ngram\": \"a time\", \"from\": 5442, \"to\": 5448}, {\"ngram\": \"dozens\", \"from\": 5453, \"to\": 5459}, {\"ngram\": \"different sports\", \"from\": 5463, \"to\": 5479}, {\"ngram\": \"sense\", \"from\": 5498, \"to\": 5503}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In our heads, we\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re just picturing, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0098My God, we might be stuck on speedwalking for an hour.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 Within about 15 minutes, we got it.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d They\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve remained nimble.\", \"from\": 5505, \"to\": 5670, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our heads\", \"from\": 5508, \"to\": 5517}, {\"ngram\": \"we\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re\", \"from\": 5519, \"to\": 5526}, {\"ngram\": \"an hour.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099\", \"from\": 5592, \"to\": 5603}, {\"ngram\": \"about 15 minutes\", \"from\": 5611, \"to\": 5627}, {\"ngram\": \"it.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d They\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve\", \"from\": 5636, \"to\": 5652}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was a popular moment on Day 9 when a crew member came on air to break down a controversy in the women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s skeet shooting final.\", \"from\": 5671, \"to\": 5804, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a popular moment\", \"from\": 5681, \"to\": 5697}, {\"ngram\": \"Day\", \"from\": 5701, \"to\": 5704}, {\"ngram\": \"a crew member\", \"from\": 5712, \"to\": 5725}, {\"ngram\": \"air\", \"from\": 5734, \"to\": 5737}, {\"ngram\": \"a controversy\", \"from\": 5752, \"to\": 5765}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Iseman says it was Collinsworth who suggested they put him on air, after observing an animated discussion in the studio.\", \"from\": 5805, \"to\": 5925, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Iseman\", \"from\": 5805, \"to\": 5811}, {\"ngram\": \"Collinsworth\", \"from\": 5824, \"to\": 5836}, {\"ngram\": \"air\", \"from\": 5867, \"to\": 5870}, {\"ngram\": \"an animated discussion\", \"from\": 5888, \"to\": 5910}, {\"ngram\": \"the studio\", \"from\": 5914, \"to\": 5924}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThere\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s no rulebook for this,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Collinsworth says.\", \"from\": 5927, \"to\": 5983, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no rulebook\", \"from\": 5940, \"to\": 5951}, {\"ngram\": \"Collinsworth\", \"from\": 5965, \"to\": 5977}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThey made a point of telling [us] that.\", \"from\": 5984, \"to\": 6026, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThey\", \"from\": 5984, \"to\": 5991}, {\"ngram\": \"a point\", \"from\": 5997, \"to\": 6004}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 6017, \"to\": 6019}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It makes you dip into your creative bag.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Iseman says fans have made the show better, too.\", \"from\": 6027, \"to\": 6120, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your creative bag.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Iseman\", \"from\": 6049, \"to\": 6077}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 6083, \"to\": 6087}, {\"ngram\": \"the show\", \"from\": 6098, \"to\": 6106}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cWe are on Twitter reading the feedback.\", \"from\": 6121, \"to\": 6163, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6134, \"end\": 6141, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5346322099023922e-37, \"text\": \"Twitter\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cWe\", \"from\": 6121, \"to\": 6126}, {\"ngram\": \"the feedback\", \"from\": 6150, \"to\": 6162}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The quadbox got better because people were saying, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0098Hey that logo\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s too big.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 We agreed.\", \"from\": 6164, \"to\": 6258, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The quadbox\", \"from\": 6164, \"to\": 6175}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 6195, \"to\": 6201}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve jumped to the six-box, we dumped the decabox.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d They\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve also gotten more interactive as they\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve found their audience.\", \"from\": 6259, \"to\": 6390, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"We\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve\", \"from\": 6259, \"to\": 6266}, {\"ngram\": \"the six-box\", \"from\": 6277, \"to\": 6288}, {\"ngram\": \"the decabox.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 6300, \"to\": 6315}, {\"ngram\": \"They\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve\", \"from\": 6316, \"to\": 6325}, {\"ngram\": \"they\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve\", \"from\": 6358, \"to\": 6367}, {\"ngram\": \"their audience\", \"from\": 6374, \"to\": 6388}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Collinsworth says when the show first started, they were hesitant to promoteGold Zoneas its own hashtag.\", \"from\": 6392, \"to\": 6496, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Collinsworth\", \"from\": 6392, \"to\": 6404}, {\"ngram\": \"the show\", \"from\": 6415, \"to\": 6423}, {\"ngram\": \"Zoneas\", \"from\": 6473, \"to\": 6479}, {\"ngram\": \"its own hashtag\", \"from\": 6480, \"to\": 6495}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt was like, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0098Nahhh let\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s do #NBCOlympics, so we\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re all on the same thing.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 But you could tell, 10 minutes into the first show, we didn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t have to [ask for] #GoldZone, we were already getting hit with it.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d People who\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve come of age during this era ofRedZoneandManningCastsand putting the Super Bowl on Nickelodeon may not realize what a change this is, or what it used to be like for Olympics fans who wanted midday updates on wrestling and water polo.\", \"from\": 6497, \"to\": 6966, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6816, \"end\": 6827, \"title\": \"htt